  - Remove conflicting statements.

  7. Validation

  - Run targeted tests for changed areas first.
  - Run full app suite:
      - npm run -w apps/jskit-value-app test
  - Fix failures and re-run until green.

  ———

  DEFINITION OF DONE

  All must be true:

  1. Every module under server/modules/* has index.js.
