  3. Top-level file/directory allowlists are satisfied.
  4. Role directories obey naming patterns.
  5. Cross-module runtime imports into internals are eliminated.
  6. Guardrails enforce this permanently.
  7. No route/schema/response regressions.
  8. Full app tests pass.

